A better summary query is to collapse into thirds:

SELECT
  CASE
    WHEN block_index <= 10 THEN 'early'
    WHEN block_index <= 20 THEN 'middle'
    ELSE 'late'
  END AS section,
  COUNT(*) AS cnt
FROM chunks
WHERE lower(label) LIKE '%california%'
GROUP BY section
ORDER BY section;
